#<ChaoticTeams>

    #<Description>

        #ChaoticTeams (v2.0) is made by LightChaosman

        #Thanks to Zububu and FromDarkHell for helping me test this on multiple occasions.

        # .

        # .

        #Most class skills will be shared among all players.

        #This means you can have a moneyshot chain on Zer0, while you have b0re, with a bit of extra bloodbath and a Wreck bonus.

        #These moneyshots will also heal your teammates since your team maya has Restoration.

        #You could get 440% movement speed bonus with 4 sirens.

        #Deathtrap and Axtons turret also reap the benefits of this. This means the turret will gain onslaught and metal storm bonus.

        # .

        #Some things don't transfer, like cloud kill.

        #Enemies also get your skills, and scale (a lot) harsher with more players.

        #That means you can create enemies with Close Enough, or rabid stalkers / vorac with 440% extra movement speed.

        #.

        #Some skills on items are also transfered, like drunk effects, orc effects, amp damage, roid damage, among others.

        # .

        #This mod will override most skill changes made in other mods.

        #This means that buffs from the UCP won't be effective in most cases.

        #Execute this mod last, to ensure everything that can be shared, gets shared.

        # .

        # .

        # Teamwork is honor / An unbreakable binding / That I must respect

    #</Description>

    #<Class Skills>

        #<Axton>

            #<Guerilla>
